        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="原理说明"><a href="#原理说明" class="headerlink" title="原理说明"></a>原理说明</h1><p>&emsp;&emsp;使用if+shell<code>source ./xxx.sh</code>命令 通过<code>KEYCHECK=$INSTALLER/common/keycheck</code>检测按键状态配合if和可视化程序块进行选择和按需调用<br>xxx.sh文件放入自己设置的目录在用<code>cd $xxx/xxx/xxx</code>即可调用<br>注意：</p><ol><li><p>./是当前目录</p></li><li><p>../是父级目录</p></li><li><p>/是根目录<br>代码如下:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">if $FUNCTION; then</span><br><span class="line">  echo -n &quot;  兼容模式    &quot; &gt;&gt;$INSTALLER/module.prop</span><br><span class="line">cd $INSTALLER/common/qita</span><br><span class="line">  source ./jian.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="开源地址"><a href="#开源地址" class="headerlink" title="开源地址"></a>开源地址</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;项目比较简单可自行看开源地址:<a href="https://gitee.com/HG666889/selectShell.git">gitee-开源传送门</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
